For over 25 years, Amstel Malta has supported our busy lifestyles by supplying us with carefully produced high-quality, nutritious beverage in stylish easy-to-hold packaging. The brand has won the hearts of Nigerians everywhere as the signature companion for any meal, and a go-to drink for all occasions. Once again, Amstel Malta has decided to excite us with two innovative developments. Not only has the brand added a new product called Amstel Malta Ultra; a no added sugar variant to its product lineup, but it have also unveiled a stylish new look that is set to provide a fresh feeling of excitement for Amstel Malta lovers everywhere. Besides its elegant revamp, this premium malt drink still remains enriched with the same amount of vitamins and minerals and provides the same well-trusted nourishment as it has for decades. So, when you go to the store to purchase your favourite malt drink, look out for the stylish new packs.<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-853928" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Amstel-Malta1.jpg.webp" alt="" width="1600" height="673" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Amstel-Malta1.jpg.webp 1600w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Amstel-Malta1-300x126.jpg.webp 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Amstel-Malta1-1024x431.jpg.webp 1024w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Amstel-Malta1-1536x646.jpg.webp 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px"> Let’s hail the latest addition to the Amstel Malta family, “Amstel Malta Ultra”; the first no added sugar malt and the first malt drink in a sleek can uniquely designed to fit the lifestyle of health-conscious Nigerians, fitness enthusiasts and people who want a light and refreshing malt diet. Amstel Malta Ultra is the perfect choice for those who want to live life to the fullest while staying healthy. So, whether or not you’re watching your sugar levels or you just like the idea of knowing you’re eating (or drinking) right, then Amstel Malta Ultra is perfect for you. And of course, if you prefer the refreshing taste of your favourite Amstel Malta, keep an eye out for the new stylish look!